name: Chapman Bags
tag_list: canvas-bags, weekend-bags, handmade-bags, fishing-bags, travel-bags, mens-shoulder-bags, car-luggage, canvas-holdalls, canvas-messenger-bag, canvas-luggage
overview:
John Chapman handmade bags are crafted in canvas, leather and tweed materials and are ideal for travel, leisure, business and sporting activities including fishing and game.

We are one of the last remaining companies to make our traditional canvas bags, leather bags and tweed bags exclusively in the UK in our own workshops in Cumbria, England.
